+you must do this, if you have any question or information you need ask before continuing(user:dann-ux, email: genisranky7@gmail.com: ---
+
+## PROGRAMMING DEPARTMENT — DELIVERABLE: VN-PROJECT BASE STRUCTURE
+
+---
+
+## PART 1 — TERMUX: REPOSITORY SETUP
+
+Execute these commands in order. Each is a single, complete command.
+
+**1. Update package list and install required tools**
+```bash
+pkg update && pkg upgrade -y
+```
+
+**2. Install Git**
+```bash
+pkg install git -y
+```
+
+**3. Navigate to home directory**
+```bash
+cd ~
+```
+
+**4. Create the project folder**
+```bash
+mkdir vn-project
+```
+
+**5. Enter the project folder**
+```bash
+cd vn-project
+```
+
+**6. Initialize Git repository**
+```bash
+git init
+```
+
+**7. Set Git identity (replace with your values)**
+```bash
+git config user.name "YourName"
+```
+
+```bash
+git config user.email "your@email.com"
+```
+
+---
+
+## PART 2 — FOLDER STRUCTURE CREATION
+
+Execute in order from inside `~/vn-project/`.
+
+**8. Create all project directories**
+```bash
+mkdir -p game images/bg images/sprites images/ui audio/music audio/sfx fonts
+```
+
+**Complete structure this produces:**
+```
+vn-project/
+├── game/
+│   ├── script.rpy
+│   ├── characters.rpy
+│   ├── variables.rpy
+│   ├── screens.rpy
+│   └── options.rpy
+├── images/
+│   ├── bg/
+│   ├── sprites/
+│   └── ui/
+├── audio/
+│   ├── music/
+│   └── sfx/
+├── fonts/
+├── .gitignore
+└── PROJECT.md
+```
+
+**9. Create .gitignore**
+```bash
+cat > .gitignore << 'EOF'
+# Ren'Py cache and build output
+game/cache/
+game/saves/
+*.rpyc
+*.rpymc
+*.pyc
+__pycache__/
+
+# Android build artifacts
+*.apk
+*.aab
+rapt/
+
+# OS junk
+.DS_Store
+Thumbs.db
+EOF
+```
+
+*Reason: `.rpyc` files are compiled from source at runtime and must not be tracked.*
+
+**10. Create PROJECT.md placeholder**
+```bash
+cat > PROJECT.md << 'EOF'
+# vn-project
+Master document lives in this file. See AI Context Prompt section for full project context.
+EOF
+```
+
+---
+
+## PART 3 — BASE .RPY FILES
+
+Execute each block in order.
+
+---
+
+**11. options.rpy**
+```bash
+cat > game/options.rpy << 'EOF'
+## options.rpy
+## Global Ren'Py configuration. Edit here to change engine-level settings.
+
+define config.name = "Camp Adventure"
+
+define config.version = "0.0.1"
+
+## Default window resolution. Can be changed before first launch.
+define config.screen_width = 1280
+define config.screen_height = 720
+
+## Save directory name on the player's device.
+define config.save_directory = "vn-project"
+
+## Window icon. Replace with final asset when available.
+# define config.window_icon = "images/ui/icon.png"
+
+## Skip transition time when developing. Set False for production.
+define config.developer = True
+
+## Default language.
+define config.language = None
+EOF
+```
+
+---
+
+**12. variables.rpy**
+```bash
+cat > game/variables.rpy << 'EOF'
+## variables.rpy
+## All global variables, flags, and relationship values are defined here.
+## This is the single source of truth for game state.
+
+## ── PROTAGONIST ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
+
+default protagonist_name = "Alex"
+default protagonist_species = "Unknown"
+
+## ── RELATIONSHIP POINTS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
+## One variable per character. Invisible to the player.
+## Convention: rel_[character_id]
+## Range: No hard cap. Narrative gates defined per character in their route.
+
+## Placeholder characters (replace IDs when characters are named)
+default rel_char1 = 0
+default rel_char2 = 0
+default rel_char3 = 0
+default rel_char4 = 0
+
+## ── BINARY FLAGS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
+## True/False variables that permanently open or close story branches.
+## Convention: flag_[description]
+
+## Example flags (expand as narrative is written)
+default flag_arrived_at_camp = False
+default flag_first_day_complete = False
+
+## ── RANDOMNESS FLAGS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
+## Randomness is rolled at game start and stored here.
+## This ensures consistency within a single playthrough.
+
+## Active characters this playthrough (populated on new game)
+default active_characters = []
+
+## Random event pool seed (set at new game start)
+default event_seed = 0
+
+## ── DAY TRACKING ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
+
+default current_day = 1
+default max_days = 14  ## Default. Randomized at game start within design range.
+EOF
+```
+
